<note id="fs-idm344249648" class="os-teacher">
<title>Standards</title>
<para id="fs-idm344736704"><emphasis effect="bold">Topic</emphasis>: 8.4 Economy after 1945</para>
<para id="fs-idm392075776"><emphasis effect="bold">Theme</emphasis>: WXT Work, Exchange, and Technology</para>
<para id="fs-idm388701248"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Objective</emphasis>: Unit 8D Explain the causes of economic growth in the years after World War II</para>
<para id="fs-idm346826624"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Development</emphasis>: 8.3.I.A</para>
<para id="fs-idm513349488"><emphasis effect="bold">Historical Thinking Skills</emphasis>: HTS-1 Developments and Processes, HTS-2 Sourcing and Situation, HTS-3 Source Claims and Evidence, HTS-4 Contextualization, HTS-5 Making Connections, HTS-6 Argumentation</para>
